#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.157:0.2"
msgid "16. Nandikkhayavagga "
msgstr "16. The End of Relishing "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 157. Bāhiranandikkhayasutta → bahiddhānandikkhayaaniccasuttaṃ (bj) | nandikkhaya 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.157:0.3"
msgid "157. Bāhiranandikkhayasutta "
msgstr "157. The Exterior and the End of Relishing "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.157:1.1"
msgid "“Anicceyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhu rūpe aniccāti passati, sāssa hoti sammādiṭṭhi. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, sights really are impermanent. A mendicant sees that they are impermanent: that’s their right view. "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.2"
msgid "Sammā passaṃ nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing rightly, they grow disillusioned. "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.3"
msgid "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo; "
msgstr "When relishing ends, greed ends. When greed ends, relishing ends. "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.4"
msgid "rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.5"
msgid "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṃ suvimuttanti vuccati. "
msgstr "When relishing and greed end, the mind is said to be well freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.157:1.6"
msgid "Anicceyeva, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sadde … "
msgstr "Sounds … "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.7"
msgid "gandhe … "
msgstr "Smells … "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.8"
msgid "rase … "
msgstr "Tastes … "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.9"
msgid "phoṭṭhabbe … "
msgstr "Touches … "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.10"
msgid "dhamme aniccāti passati, sāssa hoti sammādiṭṭhi. "
msgstr "Thoughts really are impermanent. A mendicant sees that they are impermanent: that’s their right view. "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.11"
msgid "Sammā passaṃ nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing rightly, they grow disillusioned. "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.12"
msgid "Nandikkhayā rāgakkhayo; "
msgstr "When relishing ends, greed ends. When greed ends, relishing ends. "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.13"
msgid "rāgakkhayā nandikkhayo. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn35.157:1.14"
msgid "Nandirāgakkhayā cittaṃ suvimuttanti vuccatī”ti. "
msgstr "When relishing and greed end, the mind is said to be well freed.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
